{"tid":1366743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727] 元朗狗隻部署，簡單分析","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:36:11.000Z","uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"352816e1e5cc9120d70fe630f602061624f26875","tid":1366743,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"以下喺根據以往事件嘅推斷<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 朗屏站、元朗西站，出站已經有大量狗隻，check袋check身份證</span></strong><br />\n解決方法：早啲去並改用輕鐵、巴士、或其他方法到達集合點 (自己諗，揚咗就有狗隻部署)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 去到水邊村遊樂場，出唔到大馬路，勁食胡椒噴霧</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 或者，順利俾你出到水邊村遊樂場，西面大路警力佈防，引你繼續行大馬路</span></strong><br />\na) 大馬路截擊，咁旅遊人士就會北上入咗藍絲區打巷戰 (警唔用得催淚彈？)<br />\nb) 或者，順利俾你去到南邊圍村，警力已佈防，橋下可用催淚彈、橋上狗喺制高點掃射示威者<br />\n<br />\n3b) 以往旅遊人士通常會開遮陣，拖到俾狗前後包抄，所以聽日唔好拖<br />\n<br />\n今次非常凶險<br />\n至於應唔應該去水邊村遊樂場聚人？開放俾大家討論<br />\n最緊要唔好俾狗隻估到我哋旅遊路線<br />\n去消費嘅記得留單據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=a4396d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1AMhNZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMhNZP.png&h=ac07342d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce021173deee366375b04e17f25cb4572aab1cfb","tid":1366743,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zNKOLVZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNKOLVZ.jpg&h=cbf0254f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香城Online 元朗副本逃生（離開）攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361703</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隔離post 嗰四條路，都好易俾狗截</span>"},{"